  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You infuse your weapon with blazing Chakra, sending forth a divine, burning wrath. You swing your weapon, creating a burst of flame that deals 5d8 fire damage to creatures in the area, which can deal damage to objects and set fire to combustibles.<br><br>You may opt to instead make a melee attack against a creature within melee reach. This determines the direction of the cone, and if the attack hits, the melee attack deals normal damage and has the creature hit suffer a -4 Reflex save penalty against this technique. A critical hit will not increase the damage of the cone.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d8, up to 5d8 plus 1d8 per 3 levels or 10d8 total, whichever is lower.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
